  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to describe the impact of treatment with adalimumab on work
      related productivity and economic burden in patients with Rheumatoid Arthritis (RA) treated
      in Canada.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
